data.description: Discover Your Dream home in the heart of Keswick Village in Glenside! Your quest for the perfect in-law suite ends here. This captivating Cape Cod residence offers an array of features that will leave you spellbound. Step inside to the inviting first floor, where you'll find a nice living room and plenty of natural lighting . The large eat-in kitchen is perfect for entertaining guests and hosting holiday gatherings. It's equipped with a wine fridge, brand new smart dishwasher that auto order supplies straight from Amazon, ample cabinet space, new floors, new faucet, ceramic tile backsplash, trash compactor, new garbage disposal and a new Andersen door leading you to a charming, private covered patio adorned with a brand new awning. The main floor features hardwood floors throughout, along with two cozy bedrooms, ceiling fans, and a full bathroom with new faucet and a jacuzzi-style deep tub. The master bedroom has just been upgraded with brand new closet doors. Ascend to the second floor, where you'll discover two additional bedrooms with new doors and a fresh coat of paint. But the best part is yet to come. The in-law suite in the basement has everything you could wish for. It includes a spacious living area that can double as a dining space. The updated kitchen features beautiful granite countertops, granite backsplash, beautiful cabinets, dishwasher, brand new garbage disposal, ceramic floors, and ample room to add a kitchen island. The fully updated bathroom includes a fabulous body jet spray for relaxation. Additionally, there's an extra bedroom that serves as a versatile bonus area, complete with a window and a private exit door. For your convenience, the laundry area is also located in the basement and the house is WiFi ready, including the in- law suite. Other features of this fantastic property include a one-car attached garage, a driveway for 4 to 5 cars, new roof (installed in 2021), a shed, fenced backyard, and plenty of space for children and pets to play. Plus, you're just a five-minute walk from Keswick Village, Keswick Theater, O'Neal's Food Market, and a wealth of amenities. Near all transportation. This house is an absolute gem. Don't let the opportunity to call it your home slip through your fingers. Schedule your appointment today!
